    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Software Developer',
    headLine: 'ABOUT Linda ',
    description: `I am a young motivated software developer with demonstrated work experience in a variety of
    technologies and programming languages. I love solving problems and I am looking for an opportunity whereby I will play my part as a developer and contribute
    to goal of the comapny to produce great distinctions and measureable results. And I also want to grow in my career and have impact in whatever that is required of me.

    The mere reason why I want to be a developer at SovTech is because I want to grow as a developer and also have an impact in my career, I believe sovTech has an enviroment
    whereby I can grow as a develope, enhance my skills and (Gain new skills) and contribute to any project that is given by SovTech and I also believe that SovTech has the right culture. 
    `,
    // buttonLabel: 'Get started',
